MCP Configuration
Copy the MCP configuration for your client. You must replace the placeholder with your token and optionally make adjustments for your specific MCP client and OS.

JSON config
{ [-] Collapse all
    mcpServers: { [-] Collapse all
        splunk-mcp-server: { [-] Collapse all
            command: "npx",
            args: [ [-] Collapse all
                "-y",
                "mcp-remote",
                "https://localhost:8089/services/mcp",
                "--header",
                "Authorization: Bearer <Your Token>"
            ]
        }
    }
}

